snippet.textDisplay: Everyone who is complaining about the folks who were pointing out the date misinformation along with number of increase cases.  I do not believe we did it to be aggressive or hurtful to Dr. John.  It’s just that this topic is SO extreme and we must obtain as much correct information as possible in order to prepare for our safety.  Thanks for everything you do for us Dr. John.....you’re a gem.
